MiroShark
Copyright 2026 aaronjmars
Licensed under AGPL-3.0
https://github.com/aaronjmars/MiroShark

The Neo4j storage adapter layer (neo4j-adapter/) is ported from MiroShark's
backend/app/storage/ directory. This includes the GraphStorage abstract
interface, Neo4jStorage implementation, EmbeddingService, SearchService,
NERExtractor, and neo4j_schema module. Modifications are documented in
neo4j-adapter/README.md.

